(95, 'AH!', 'Hermitage of the Awakened Heart, North Wales', 'Week, Retreat,Teachings', 'Lama Shenpen Hookham', 'An exploration of the power of sounds, words and mantras, including how to use them in practice to evoke and connect to the power of Awakening.', 'AH! An exploration of the power of sounds, words and mantras, including how to use them in practice to evoke and connect to the power of Awakening.', '2004-08-07T00:00:00'),
