(43, 'Meditation', 'Trigonos, North Wales', 'Week, Retreat,Teachings', 'Lama Shenpen Hookham', 'The emphasis in this retreat will be on deepening our meditation, so as well as plenty of sitting and walking meditation, there will be step by step teachings and exploration of how to work with the meditation instructions', '', '2002-10-26T00:00:00'),
(57, 'Experience is Alove', 'Trigonos, North Wales', 'Week, Retreat,Teachings', 'Lama Shenpen Hookham', 'In our practice we feel that we are discovering some truth within ourselves. But the true nature of our experience is so alive that perhaps this truth is also discovering us.', '', '2003-03-29T00:00:00'),
(58, 'Effort and Effortlessness', 'Trigonos, North Wales', 'Week, Retreat,Teachings', 'Lama Shenpen Hookham', 'Exploring the meaning of effortlessness in meditation and awareness practice and how to square this with the obvious need fr perseverance and discipline.', '', '2003-08-16T00:00:00'),
(82, 'The Body as an Expression of Awareness', 'Trigonos, North Wales', 'Week, Retreat,Teachings', 'Lama Shenpen Hookham', 'Using physical movement to discover aspects of awareness that we might otherwise miss, so that we can connect more easily to our natural sensitivity and responsiveness.', 'The Body as an Expression of Awareness. Using physical movement to discover aspects of awareness that we might otherwise miss,┬áso that we can connect more easily to our natural sensitivity and responsiveness in our meditation and daily life practice.', '2004-04-17T00:00:00'),
